===message:The civil war was like a very dramatic version of a fight between sibilings.  I know that my sister and I had small fights growing up, but in our late teens we had one huge blow up over a small issue that had been festering between us.  The fight lasted about a week and almost drove our parents out of the house but when it was over we were the best of friends and have always supported each other.  We both learned lessons from our fight and we grew as people.  Our nation learned many lessons from our internal fight and grew into a strong country.
